TY  - JOUR
TI  - Instrumental Models and Indirect Encompassing
AU  - Dhaene, Geert
AU  - Gourieroux, Christian
AU  - Scaillet, Oliver
AB  - [We introduce nonnested hypotheses tests using indirect, simulation-based estimation procedures. We propose different test statistics and carefully examine the corresponding implicit null hypotheses. A notion of indirect encompassing comes up naturally, which may be compared to the usual encompassing conditions. Then we show how these methods extend standard specification and overidentification tests.]
